# /. 1 Overview
**************

EasyPG Assistant is an Emacs frontend application to GnuPG (GNU Privacy
Guard) that provides the following features:

   • Key management.
   • Cryptographic operations on regions.
   • Cryptographic operations on files.
   • Dired integration.
   • Mail-mode integration.
   • Automatic encryption/decryption of *.gpg files.


